==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fleabane
<hw>Flea"bane`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>One of various plants, supposed to have efficacy in driving away
fleas. They belong, for the most part, to the genera <gen>Conyza</gen>,
<gen>Erigeron</gen>, and <gen>Pulicaria</gen>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Flea-beetle</ent>⟦br⟧
